{"nodes": [{"id": "context_aktivitaet", "label": "Aktivit\u00e4t (Domain Concept)", "file_type": "rationale", "source_file": "CONTEXT.md", "source_location": "lines 7-9", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Eine Moodle-Aktivit\u00e4t mit eindeutiger activityId und eigener Widget-Konfiguration. Zentrales Organisationselement f\u00fcr Chat-Sessions und Kosten."}, {"id": "context_widget_konfiguration", "label": "Widget-Konfiguration (Domain Concept)", "file_type": "rationale", "source_file": "CONTEXT.md", "source_location": "lines 11-13", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Konfigurierbare Felder (botTitle, botIcon, uploadMode, opener, hints, task, taskImage) auf drei Ebenen: Systemvorlage \u2192 Lehrer-Vorlage \u2192 Aktivit\u00e4tskonfiguration. Jede Ebene \u00fcberschreibt die dar\u00fcber liegende."}, {"id": "context_systemvorlage", "label": "Systemvorlage (Domain Concept)", "file_type": "rationale", "source_file": "CONTEXT.md", "source_location": "lines 15-17", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Vom Admin festgelegte Standardwerte. Gilt f\u00fcr Lehrkr\u00e4fte ohne eigene Lehrer-Vorlage."}, {"id": "context_lehrer_vorlage", "label": "Lehrer-Vorlage (Domain Concept)", "file_type": "rationale", "source_file": "CONTEXT.md", "source_location": "lines 19-21", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Von einer Lehrkraft festgelegte Standardwerte. \u00dcberschreibt Systemvorlage, gilt als Ausgangswert f\u00fcr neue Aktivit\u00e4ten dieser Lehrkraft."}, {"id": "context_erfahrungsprompt", "label": "Erfahrungsprompt (Domain Concept)", "file_type": "rationale", "source_file": "CONTEXT.md", "source_location": "lines 23-25", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Aktivit\u00e4tsspezifischer Zusatz zum globalen Systemprompt. Max. 200 W\u00f6rter. Entsteht aus Feedback und Simulation, wird automatisch in den Prompt-Stack eingebunden."}, {"id": "context_persona", "label": "Persona (Domain Concept)", "file_type": "rationale", "source_file": "CONTEXT.md", "source_location": "lines 27-29", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Profil eines fiktiven Sch\u00fclers f\u00fcr Simulationen. Kann global (Admin), lehrerspezifisch oder aus echten Sch\u00fcler-Chats generiert werden."}, {"id": "context_simulation", "label": "Simulation (Domain Concept)", "file_type": "rationale", "source_file": "CONTEXT.md", "source_location": "lines 31-33", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Automatisierter Testlauf: Persona generiert synthetische \u00c4u\u00dferungen, Prompt-Stack antwortet, Antworten werden anhand von Kriterien bewertet. Ergebnis: Simulations-Paare."}, {"id": "context_kriterien", "label": "Kriterien (Domain Concept)", "file_type": "rationale", "source_file": "CONTEXT.md", "source_location": "lines 35-37", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Pr\u00fcfbare Aussagen zur Bewertung von KI-Antworten in Simulationen. Werden aus dem Prompt abgeleitet oder manuell definiert."}, {"id": "context_erkenntnis", "label": "Erkenntnis (Domain Concept)", "file_type": "rationale", "source_file": "CONTEXT.md", "source_location": "lines 39-41", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Aus Simulations-Ergebnissen destillierte Beobachtung, die in zuk\u00fcnftigen Optimierungsvorschl\u00e4gen ber\u00fccksichtigt wird."}, {"id": "context_one_click_optimierung", "label": "One-Click-Optimierung (Domain Concept)", "file_type": "rationale", "source_file": "CONTEXT.md", "source_location": "lines 43-45", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Automatisierter Ablauf: Kriterien vorschlagen \u2192 mehrere Personas parallel simulieren \u2192 Erfahrungsprompt-Verbesserungsvorschlag generieren. Ausgeliefert als SSE-Stream."}, {"id": "context_plenumsphase", "label": "Plenumsphase (Domain Concept)", "file_type": "rationale", "source_file": "CONTEXT.md", "source_location": "lines 47-49", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Zustand in dem der Chat f\u00fcr alle Sch\u00fcler einer Aktivit\u00e4t gesperrt ist. Vom Lehrer ausgel\u00f6st, optional mit automatischer Entsperrung nach N Minuten."}, {"id": "widget_config_inheritance", "label": "Widget Configuration Inheritance Pattern", "file_type": "rationale", "source_file": "CONTEXT.md", "source_location": "lines 11-13", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Three-tier override chain: Systemvorlage \u2192 Lehrer-Vorlage \u2192 Aktivit\u00e4tskonfiguration. Each level overrides the one above. Enables per-activity customization while providing sensible defaults."}], "edges": [{"source": "context_widget_konfiguration", "target": "context_systemvorlage", "relation": "conceptually_related_to", "confidence": "EXTRACTED", "confidence_score": 1.0, "source_file": "CONTEXT.md", "source_location": null, "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "context_widget_konfiguration", "target": "context_lehrer_vorlage", "relation": "conceptually_related_to", "confidence": "EXTRACTED", "confidence_score": 1.0, "source_file": "CONTEXT.md", "source_location": null, "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "context_widget_konfiguration", "target": "context_aktivitaet", "relation": "conceptually_related_to", "confidence": "EXTRACTED", "confidence_score": 1.0, "source_file": "CONTEXT.md", "source_location": null, "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "context_simulation", "target": "context_persona", "relation": "references", "confidence": "EXTRACTED", "confidence_score": 1.0, "source_file": "CONTEXT.md", "source_location": null,